image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/247_Sensor_Modus_2.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"2afdc50f-145a-40cd-9161-258a892f32a9":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19884972900676__2afdc50f-145a-40cd-9161-258a892f32a9-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h5><strong>Kwaliteit & Batterijduur<\/strong><\/h5><h5><\/h5><p>De batterij is in 3 uur tijd volledig opgeladen en gaat 3 maanden lang mee! Bij rood licht laad de lamp op, bij groen licht is de batterij vol, Heel gemakkelijk!<\/p><p>De Roolo LED-Lamp bestaat uit een aluminium behuizing en is daardoor super licht. Daarnaast beschermt de hoogwaardige coating het tegen snel krassen en is daardoor ook een echte <em>eye-catcher<\/em><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19884972900676__2afdc50f-145a-40cd-9161-258a892f32a9-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":32}},"fb0ea45e-9026-463a-8038-4bee6f8f1efa":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Scherm_afbeelding_2023-10-10_om_22.29.06.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"495da2e8-6942-45a8-96d8-2bf29b5505e6":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19884972900676__495da2e8-6942-45a8-96d8-2bf29b5505e6-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h5><strong>Geschikt voor elke kamer!<\/strong><\/h5><p><\/p><p>De Roolo LED-Lamp is geschikt voor elke kamer, of u de lamp nou gebruikt om meer licht te hebben in de keuken, een nachtelijke wandeling door het huis te maken, sfeer te creëren op uw bureau of om een schilderij te belichten, onze lamp kan het allemaal!<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19884972900676__495da2e8-6942-45a8-96d8-2bf29b5505e6-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":4}},"7ead9d52-a3ce-4f63-9e00-e5fbe252c5a8":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Scherm_afbeelding_2023-10-10_om_22.48.56.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"c3fa4cb6-a302-472c-97c9-d43a96ccddb1":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_foto.webp","height":"medium","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--19810270937412__01e44fca-e5d3-4b7e-a501-4420559a80d3-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"HANDLEIDING","icon":"none","row_content":"<p><strong>Altijd AAN modus: <\/strong>eenmaal op de knop drukken.<\/p><p><strong>Alleen Nacht modus: <\/strong>Dubbel klikken om alleen 's nachts bewegingssensoren in te schakelen. (handig voor bijvoorbeeld het toilet)<\/p><p><strong>Dag & Nacht modus: <\/strong>3 keer klikken op de knop, sensoren zijn nu de hele dag en nacht ingeschakeld.<\/p><p><strong>Licht opties: <\/strong>Druk eenmaal op de licht knop om te schakelen tussen warm, neutraal en wit licht. Houd de knop ingedrukt om de helderheid aan te passen.<\/p>","page":""}},"1f602d09-7ba6-44a2-b52b-04db4e4d7e42":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Maten","i